datasets.name: eb85db02
queryLines:
SELECT 
  t1.*,
  t1.input_token_count + t1.output_token_count as total_token_count,
  t2.endpoint_name,
  t2.endpoint_id,
  t2.served_entity_name,
  t2.entity_type
FROM system.serving.endpoint_usage t1
INNER JOIN system.serving.served_entities t2 ON
  t1.served_entity_id = t2.served_entity_id

datasets.name: c929de80
queryLines:
SELECT 
  t1.account_id,
  t1.workspace_id,
  t1.record_id,
  t1.sku_name,
  t1.usage_date,
  t1.usage_start_time,
  t1.usage_end_time,
  t1.usage_quantity,
  t2.pricing.default as price,
  t2.pricing.default * t1.usage_quantity as dbu_cost,
  t1.usage_metadata.endpoint_id as endpoint_id,
  t1.usage_metadata.endpoint_name as endpoint_name,
  t1.billing_origin_product,
  t1.product_features.serving_type as serving_type,
  t1.usage_type,
  t2.price_start_time,
  t2.price_end_time
FROM system.billing.usage t1
INNER JOIN system.billing.list_prices t2 ON
  t1.sku_name = t2.sku_name 
  AND t1.account_id = t2.account_id
  AND t1.usage_date >= date(t2.price_start_time)
  AND t1.usage_date <= coalesce(date(t2.price_end_time), to_date('2099-12-31'))
WHERE 
  t1.usage_type in ('TOKEN', 'ANSWER');
